{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t15-train-2","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"有理数的运算","title":"针对训练2：差倒数问题","difficulty":5,"tags":["新定义","规律","周期"],"content":"已知 $a$ 为不等于 1 的有理数，我们把 $\\frac{1}{1-a}$ 叫做 $a$ 的差倒数。\n\n若 $a_1 = -3$，$a_2$ 是 $a_1$ 的差倒数，$a_3$ 是 $a_2$ 的差倒数，...，以此类推。\n\n(1) 求 $a_2$、$a_3$、$a_4$；\n(2) 若 $a_1 = -3$ 的差倒数是 $a_2$，$a_2$ 的差倒数是 $a_3$，...，依此类推，则 $a_{2025} = $ ______。","steps":[{"title":"计算前几项","content":"$a_1 = -3$\n$a_2 = \\frac{1}{1-(-3)} = \\frac{1}{4}$\n$a_3 = \\frac{1}{1-\\frac{1}{4}} = \\frac{1}{\\frac{3}{4}} = \\frac{4}{3}$\n$a_4 = \\frac{1}{1-\\frac{4}{3}} = \\frac{1}{-\\frac{1}{3}} = -3 = a_1$","formula":""},{"title":"找规律","content":"发现周期为 3：$a_1 = -3, a_2 = \\frac{1}{4}, a_3 = \\frac{4}{3}, a_4 = -3, ...$\n\n$2025 = 3 \\times 675$，余数为 0\n\n$a_{2025} = a_3 = \\frac{4}{3}$","formula":"\\text{答案：}\\frac{4}{3}"}]},"id":"t15-train-2"},"__N_SSG":true}